OL,3,CWelsh speaking areas to get extra
OL,4,Cgovernment support in language push
OL,6,FThe Welsh government has unveiled
OL,7,Ffresh measures aimed at halting the
OL,8,Fdecline of the Welsh language, but
OL,9,Fsome of the measures they plan to take
OL,10,Fcould be controversial, ITV News Wales
OL,11,FReporter Rhys Williams reports
OL,13,FLatest census data showed a small
OL,14,Fdecline in the number of Welsh
OL,15,Fspeakers in Wales from 19% to 17.8%.
OL,17,FBut a big rise in the number of
OL,18,Fchildren speaking Welsh in Cardiff
OL,19,Fmeant the true loss of the language in
OL,20,Fits historical heartlands was masked.
