OL,3,CWelsh speaking areas to get extra
OL,4,Cgovernment support in language push
OL,6,FThey argue that housing developments
OL,7,Fwith insufficient affordable homes, as
OL,8,Fwell as the proliferation of second
OL,9,Fhomes, inflates property prices and
OL,10,Freduces the number of Welsh-speaking
OL,11,Ffamilies able to stay in these areas.
OL,13,FNow, the Welsh government has
OL,14,Fannounced plans to give protected
OL,15,Fstatus to some Welsh speaking
OL,16,Fcommunities akin to special
OL,17,Fconservation areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
