OL,3,CWelsh speaking areas to get extra
OL,4,Cgovernment support in language push
OL,6,FThat would mean developers and local
OL,7,Fauthorities will have to increase the
OL,8,Fconsideration given to the Welsh
OL,9,Flanguage when applications are made.
OL,11,FThe Welsh government's Secretary for
OL,12,Fthe Welsh Language, Mark Drakeford,
OL,13,Ftold me he accepts this policy may
OL,14,Flead to more developments being
OL,15,Fblocked, but says it's a matter of
OL,16,F"levelling the playing field" for
OL,17,Flocal residents.
